parent1.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with shimmering feathers in the style of expressionist art. It hovers in mid-air above a tranquil lagoon surrounded by towering ancient trees at dawn, trailing sparks of golden fire from its wings amidst an environment of moss-covered statues and bioluminescent mushrooms.

offspring.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with iridescent feathers in the style of expressionist art. It hovers above a tranquil lagoon surrounded by ancient trees at dawn, trailing sparks of golden fire from its wings amidst an environment of moss-covered statues and bioluminescent mushrooms.
